rows.label: tlk401003_msg0002
rows.name:
Myself, I am Superbian, yet I live
under the protection of Acedia.

rows.label: tlk401003_msg0003
rows.name:
And the Invidians and Gulan
here, for instance, seem to get
along just as well.

rows.label: tlk401003_msg0004
rows.name: But just take a look at those lot.

rows.label: tlk401003_msg0005
rows.name:
Clutching their tools of conflict,
and fixing one another with the
coldest of stares...

rows.label: tlk401003_msg0006
rows.name:
They can't even have a civil discussion
short of holding a banquet like this.

rows.label: tlk401003_msg0008
rows.name:
If they have the time to be wasting on
such extravagances, they should use
it to save their own suffering people.

rows.label: tlk401003_msg0009
rows.name:
It does frustrate me. Sometimes I think
the people running those nations could
learn a thing or two from our camp.
